In his first lecture to a group of South vietnamese officers, MTF took several minutes to tell his favorite joke. The interpreter translated, using only a few words.<br>
After the lecture MTF asked the interpreter how he had been able to tell such a long joke so quickly.<br>
&quot;Well, sir,&quot; confessed the Vietnamese interpreter,<br>
&quot;I didn't think anyone would get the point so I just said,<br>
&quot;MTF has told a joke, Everyone will please laugh.&quot;<br>

